{"tid":175694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個細個老豆老用咩體罰你","createTime":"2017-03-27T16:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T18:49:42.000Z","uid":17521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b0a933ad5d10dc4c14be0973770041795dd6956","tid":175694,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"以前係日本買左枝用黎揼骨嘅按摩棒<br />\n<br />\n老豆個陣攞左個枝野嚟打我<br />\n<br />\n仲記得個陣好撚痛，佢越打我越火滾<br />\n<br />\n我就一手搶左枝野分開左個按摩頭同枝棍，好撚型咁左右拋開<br />\n<br />\n自此之後老豆冇再打我 勇武抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申個陣得大約12歲"},{"pid":"6b2b7984c5a250ac8e4d4691dfbf51f936577579","tid":175694,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"佢。。。佢。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979f2079579bae74c73a01c05b884f64f8ecc853","tid":175694,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"有睇鬼父既 應該就明白我老豆罰我既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58486e8a8e5e2f8b08e3209049d0a4f763c69ff9","tid":175694,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"打緊機成部ps2兜面車埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bbd4060bbf90632620d75431ee79a60c102d8f","tid":175694,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打緊機成部ps2兜面車埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n車部PS2去你塊面度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我平時瞓低用電話成部電話跌落塊面都覺得好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66992390eead6a7de446f04a15a461af902fd504","tid":175694,"uid":31530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci