ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0640ff0927d65eeb79b6ab8f4c840e2070c1f288","tid":175694,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>風扇<br />\n<br />\n你冇睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係風扇<br />\n<br />\n成個車埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇毀容</blockquote><br />\n咁啱條電線扯實<br />\n<br />\n食咗一半力"},{"pid":"4c5e89f118865311259d3c58857e313c94204611","tid":175694,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:33:31.000Z","msg":"鼓棍"},{"pid":"8b8fc5c38b22ee977e40b00b9ac8bedeb9148bbd","tid":175694,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個同表哥出夜街 唔記得做咩 可能覺得我細唔可以出夜街 攞條濕毛巾抽我塊面 勁撚痛</blockquote><br />\n幾夜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377781ec831b516ea086e21dc489108da08dc8bd","tid":175694,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"幼稚園做功課鳩hea<br />\n成把剪刀飛過黎,插中鼻樑位附近，而家果個位都有少少痕<br />\n自己完全唔記得件，以為果個位係雀班之類既野。<br />\n係幾年前拜山同親戚傾先知有件咁既事。"},{"pid":"06301107a32069401d078828e7e1d325b6bf8f43","tid":175694,"uid":20605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個同表哥出夜街 唔記得做咩 可能覺得我細唔可以出夜街 攞條濕毛巾抽我塊面 勁撚痛</blockquote><br />\n幾夜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該兩點幾 個陣返到屋企我都知唔對路㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96371736adf4caf3b1b841657ef9da55667ca1a","tid":175694,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前係日本買左枝用黎揼骨嘅按摩棒<br />\n<br />\n老豆個陣攞左個枝野嚟打我<br />\n<br />\n仲記得個陣好撚痛，佢越打我越火滾<br />\n<br />\n我就一手搶左枝野分開左個按摩頭同枝棍，好撚型咁左右拋開<br />\n<br />\n自此之後老豆冇再打我 勇武抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申個陣得大約12歲</blockquote><br />\n12歲仲有體罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我阿媽話返俾我知 我老豆係我好細個（頂多K3）嚇我話唔要我<br />\n<br />\n跟住抱我去後樓梯上左兩層樓放低左我 佢自己好快走返完本個層 點知我嚇到飛起想追返佢 係樓梯跌到仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我印象中就冇俾老豆體罰過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nF.1,f.2個陣好似仲有，其實身教好過體罰好多，唔覺體罰會乖左"},{"pid":"6a8e22a3228a18548ffb57ef332f66556088ce17","tid":175694,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個同表哥出夜街 唔記得做咩 可能覺得我細唔可以出夜街 攞條濕毛巾抽我塊面 勁撚痛</blockquote><br />\n幾夜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該兩點幾 個陣返到屋企我都知唔對路㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估我去到17先夠膽兩三點返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a59148666ef7a462e3ae48bbed3eb88b8bd4be","tid":175694,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幼稚園做功課鳩hea<br />\n成把剪刀飛過黎,插中鼻樑位附近，而家果個位都有少少痕<br />\n自己完全唔記得件事，以為果個位係雀班之類既野。<br />\n係幾年前拜山同親戚傾先知有件咁既事。</blockquote><br />\n把剪刀件仲要係製衣果種剪刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c5eca142dde12d8a23c0ac4aa4a8590e83211e","tid":175694,"uid":46085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"用火機燒"},{"pid":"0c204c5423fb2a3b382f43e1bc93e87abf275b05","tid":175694,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"今次化第幾屆鬥慘大會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124528918ce64a3f7ec86c9297d7c50acf6997dd","tid":175694,"uid